i></ul><h1 class="sc-4868f6b2-0 kxCvEg">The Heat Goes On: 2024 Starts Out Record Warm</h1><h2 class="sc-44728060-0 kvvjnQ">After 2023 blew the roof off the record for warmest year, January has now gone into the record books too.</h2><div class="sc-47c53dda-0 bePCqU"><div><span><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/cnu0m8re1exe/4X6GxZcHKLREwtVWl9ys4e/7a94cfa7d2df8289ba0c359318932796/imageo_75.png?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;w=24&amp;h=24&amp;fit=fill" alt="ImaGeo icon" class="sc-e706b2c9-0 bjhdPu sc-fafb1cae-0 DhiES" height="24px" width="24px"/><a class="sc-acb0869a-0 cgZEsQ" href="/blog/imageo">ImaGeo</a></span></div><div><span class="sc-2fa50208-0 fuTWQQ">By <a class="sc-acb0869a-0 cgZEsQ" href="/author/tomyulsman">Tom Yulsman</a></span></div><div><span class="sc-73638515-0 gguonj">Feb 16, 2024 1:15 AM</span><span class="sc-92d150c4-0 kmluij">Feb 17, 2024 1:56 AM</span></div></div></div><div class="sc-87d213a0-0 gdbaPI"><div style="display:flex"><div class="sc-4abb9ce9-0 kGGzyr"><div class="sc-5fc35b96-0 llLGAK"><button class="react-share__ShareButton" style="background-color:transparent;border:none;padding:0;font:inherit;color:inherit;cursor:pointer"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="32" height="32"><rect width="64" height="64" rx="0" ry="0" fill="#0965FE"></rect><path d="M34.1,47V33.3h4.6l0.7-5.3h-5.3v-3.4c0-1.5,0.4-2.6,2.6-2.6l2.8,0v-4.8c-0.5-0.1-2.2-0.2-4.1-0.2 c-4.1,0-6.9,2.5-6.9,7V28H24v5.3h4.6V47H34.1z" fill="white"></path></svg></button><button class="react-share__ShareButton" style="background-color:transparent;border:none;padding:0;font:inherit;color:inherit;cursor:pointer"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="32" height="32"><rect width="64" height="64" rx="0" ry="0" fill="#000000"></rect><path d="M 41.116 18.375 h 4.962 l -10.8405 12.39 l 12.753 16.86 H 38.005 l -7.821 -10.2255 L 21.235 47.625 H 16.27 l 11.595 -13.2525 L 15.631 18.375 H 25.87 l 7.0695 9.3465 z m -1.7415 26.28 h 2.7495 L 24.376 21.189 H 21.4255 z" fill="white"></path></svg></button><button class="